{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"escape 和 unescape 函數","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Functions_ceaa4b2a55bb67388c2728af1ff890f5","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"onlyinclude\" id=\"sect1\">\n<h4 id=\"escape_和_unescape_函數\">escape 和 unescape 函數</h4>\n<p><code>escape</code> 和 <code>unescape</code> 函數可讓你把字串編碼或解碼。<code>escape</code> 函數會返回以 ISO Latin 字元集來表示參數的十六進制編碼。<code>unescape</code> 函數會對指定的十六進制編碼值返回 ASCII 字串。</p>\n<p>這些函數的語句是︰</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">escape(string)\nunescape(string)\n</pre>\n<p>這些函數主要是在伺服端的 JavaScript 用來編碼或解碼 URL 裡的名稱和值的配對。</p>\n<p><code>escape</code> 和 <code>unescape</code> 函數在非 ASCII 字元下無法正確運作，也已被廢棄。在 JavaScript 1.5 及其後版本中，可以改用 <code><a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_參考/全域函數/encodeURI\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 參考/全域函數/encodeURI\">encodeURI</a></code>、<code><a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_參考/全域函數/decodeURI\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 參考/全域函數/decodeURI\">decodeURI</a></code>、<code><a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_參考/全域函數/encodeURIComponent\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 參考/全域函數/encodeURIComponent\">encodeURIComponent</a></code>、<code><a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_參考/全域函數/decodeURIComponent\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 參考/全域函數/decodeURIComponent\">decodeURIComponent</a></code>。</p>\n</div>\n<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/預先定義的函數/Number_和_String_函數\">« 前頁</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/閉鎖的運用\">次頁  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"escape 和 unescape 函數可讓你把字串編碼或解碼。escape 函數會返回以 ISO Latin 字元集來表示參數的十六進制編碼。unescape 函數會對指定的十六進制編碼值返回 ASCII 字串。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"locale":"en-US","title":"Functions","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/functions_ceaa4b2a55bb67388c2728af1ff890f5","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/functions_ceaa4b2a55bb67388c2728af1ff890f5/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide","title":"陣列的運用"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Functions_ceaa4b2a55bb67388c2728af1ff890f5","title":"escape 和 unescape 函數"}],"pageTitle":"escape 和 unescape 函數 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}